        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "彼女は悲しみの形を顔に浮かべていた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "子供の頃の写真を見ていると、幼い頃の父の形が思い出される。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "初めて会う人の形から、その人の性格を推し量ろうとする。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 3,
        "gloss": "form (as opposed to substance)",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "彼は会社の形だけ整えて、実質的な経営は他人に任せている。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "会議は形だけで、すでに決定事項が用意されていた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "いくら形を整えても、中身が伴わなければ意味がない。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 4,
        "gloss": "(resultant) state",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "災害後、街は見るも無残な形になっていた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "交渉は難航し、最終的には合意に至らない形となった。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "彼の助言のおかげで、事態は良い形に収まった。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 5,
        "gloss": "behaviour (towards others)",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "どんなに忙しくても、人にはきちんと挨拶する形を崩してはいけない。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "彼は困っている人に手を差し伸べる、優しい形をしている。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "部下を叱る時も、相手を傷つけない形を選ぶべきだ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 6,
        "gloss": "shape (positional qualities of a group of stones)",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "囲碁の対局では、相手の石の形を良く見ることが勝利への鍵となる。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "この形では、次にどこに打つべきか判断が難しい。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "悪い形を直すには、一度手を引く勇気も必要だ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      }
